ingredients - Ingredient Management

USAGE:
    ingredients <action>

DESCRIPTION:
    Manage recipe ingredients. Various operations for working with
    ingredient lists and meal planning.

ACTIONS:
    list
        List all ingredients

    scale
        Scale ingredient quantities

    unique
        Find unique ingredients

    units
        Manage ingredient units

    shopping
        Generate shopping list

EXAMPLES:
    ingredients list
    ingredients scale
    ingredients unique
    ingredients units
    ingredients shopping
